mediaItems.title: Was craving my favorite salad from my favorite restaurant in Ann Arbor so I went and got it for lunch! I did have a little food issue because I forgot to order my salad without cheese or bread. I've been eating really well, and didn't want to ruin my pattern. So when I got it, I was like OH NO I can't eat that, and started to try to eat around the cheese. Then I realized how ridiculous that was and just thought, "Why the heck am I not allowed to have a little bread and cheese once in a while?" My obsessive nature about what I eat, and not allowing myself to have the things I like in moderation was what brought me down the wrong path with food before. So you know what? I ate that bread and cheese and it was AWESOME. I'm continuing to learn how to live my life with moderation, and I'm getting better every day. Moral of the story, when life hands you bread and cheese, eat it. #lunch #lunchtime #food #healthyfood #healthylunch #takethatED #salad #chicken #cheese #bread #annarbor #highprotein #health #healthy #fitness #fit #eatthecheese #fitlikeaqueen
